Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark XI的狀態呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在保護運輸艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我還沒辦法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛翔 - 犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,45區地面受害範圍擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強防衛機制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻擋它的行動！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人到達亞爾維斯裝甲外牆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B1-45區塊中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標持續朝正下方攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的目標是女神之巖嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神之巖似乎啟動了專用防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有四架諾倫被擊落了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法阻止人面獅身型的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D9-8區塊發生火災 啟動消防系統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會保護你的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就約好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B3已封閉至第25區塊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾倫進入波狀攻擊體制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神之巖正上方已被破壞至第9區塊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第18 24 26號自律迎擊系統沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中人面獅身型 但是並沒有消滅它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼穿上協同作用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在打什麼主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去跟它戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要保護這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓妳為了這座島而去冒這種險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是為了這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了一騎啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 使用伏狼刀索！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子 妳的身體太虛弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就根本是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是打從出生就注定要戰鬥了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想以我自己的意願去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小事應該能被允許吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我又不是妳的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起她就是妳的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟一騎已經約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要遵守我的諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟一騎承受一樣的痛楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會啟動？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間 是誰啟動Mark VI的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？要出動Mark VI？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你阻止翔子吧 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護這座島是我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且羽佐間翔子是最適合駕駛Mark VI的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也很清楚吧 羽佐間老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間 出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…翔子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推進動力平衡有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Mark VI暫時回航
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要重新調整推進引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您住口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准對大人下令！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾維斯內部受損擴大到B4-86區塊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI從上空接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾維斯危險了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是API-1法夫那的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾出一騎的島！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間 戰鬥匕首是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦波開始產生混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI也行不通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的羽佐間 羽佐間！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把它從這座島上拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在上空就交給諾倫攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了 快離開異界體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了 羽佐間？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我甩不開…\N-什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快逃離啊 羽佐間！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用「魔狼」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼認證通過 魔狼啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法執行魔狼解除密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 我會保護你的島…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做傻事啊 翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…把翔子還給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-甲洋！\N-春日井
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,候補駕駛員都必須待命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准擅自離開工作崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔狼解放等級設定為最高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 媽媽 是媽媽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 為什麼我叫做翔子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我希望妳能在天空翱翔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在天上飛的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片天空中翱翔嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我又不是妳的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不該那樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣…有遵守約定了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…是怎樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI…跟異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起消滅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是騙人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的吧…翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟貴重的Mark VI一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起頭來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天雖然晴朗卻下了場雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:22:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而她輕輕撐開笑容的傘 遞給被雨淋濕的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且說著「天空啊 別再哭泣了…」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在空中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急於戰鬥的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表現出憤怒的是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而流下淚來的也是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們只是被絕望的雨淋濕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「蒼穹之戰神」第7話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家賊 - 親子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
